#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-23-mkdocs-mkdocstrings-githubio.rst:9
msgid "MkDocs + mkdocstrings で Python コード連動のドキュメントを公開"
msgstr "Publish Python code-linked documentation with MkDocs + mkdocstrings"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-23-mkdocs-mkdocstrings-githubio.rst:11
msgid ""
"Python のコードから自動で API ドキュメントを生成し、それを MkDocs を使って GitHub Pages "
"上に公開するまでの体験を行ったので、その手順と感想をまとめておきます。"
msgstr ""
"I experienced automatically generating API documentation from Python code "
"and publishing it on GitHub Pages using MkDocs, so I would like to summarize"
" the steps and impressions."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-23-mkdocs-mkdocstrings-githubio.rst:18
msgid "概要"
msgstr "overview"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-23-mkdocs-mkdocstrings-githubio.rst:20
msgid "使用ツール: MkDocs, mkdocstrings, Poetry"
msgstr "Tools used: MkDocs, mkdocstrings, Poetry"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-23-mkdocs-mkdocstrings-githubio.rst:21
msgid "目的: Python コードの docstring を API ドキュメントとして Markdown 上に展開し、公開まで一貫して試すこと"
msgstr ""
"Purpose: Deploy Python code docstrings as API documentation on Markdown and "
"try them out until publishing."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-23-mkdocs-mkdocstrings-githubio.rst:22
msgid "成果: 関数の引数・戻り値などが表形式で整然と表示される見やすいドキュメントを作成・公開できた"
msgstr ""
"Results: We were able to create and publish an easy-to-read document that "
"displays function arguments, return values, etc. in an orderly manner in a "
"table format."

