#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-23-mkdocs-mkdocstrings-githubio.rst:79
msgid "感想"
msgstr "thoughts"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-23-mkdocs-mkdocstrings-githubio.rst:81
msgid "docstring が自動で整形され、非常に見やすい表形式で API 仕様が表示されるのが便利"
msgstr ""
"Conveniently formats the docstring automatically and displays the API "
"specification in a very easy-to-read tabular format."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-23-mkdocs-mkdocstrings-githubio.rst:82
msgid "Markdown ベースで編集できるため、Sphinx よりも導入・修正が簡単に感じた"
msgstr ""
"Since it can be edited based on Markdown, I felt it was easier to install "
"and modify than Sphinx."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-23-mkdocs-mkdocstrings-githubio.rst:83
msgid "コードとの連動性が高く、変更があってもドキュメントにすぐ反映できる安心感がある"
msgstr ""
"It is highly linked with the code, and there is a sense of security that any"
" changes can be immediately reflected in the document."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-23-mkdocs-mkdocstrings-githubio.rst:84
msgid "`mkdocstrings` を通じて、型ヒントや Google-style docstring の価値も改めて実感した"
msgstr ""
"Through `mkdocstrings`, I realized once again the value of type hints and "
"Google-style docstrings."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-23-mkdocs-mkdocstrings-githubio.rst:86
msgid "今後は、この構成をテンプレート化したり、CI連携で自動更新の仕組みも導入していきたい。"
msgstr ""
"In the future, we would like to create a template for this configuration and"
" introduce an automatic update mechanism through CI coordination."

